\v 23 \x + \xo 2:23: \xt Deu 23:25.\x*And it so happened that Yeshua andÂŠ23232 hisÂŠ23253 followers passed through some fields of grain on some daysÂŠ23239 of rest. As they went through, they pluckedÂŠ23258 off some headsÂŠ23261 of grain.
