\p
\v 5 After angrily looking aroundÂŠ23476 at them, grievingÂŠ23481 at theirÂŠ23488 complete lack of compassion, he said to the man, â\wj Open up yourÂŠ23495 hand!\wj*â
\v 6 The man stretched out his fingers, and his hand became totally normal. ButÂŠ23509 the Pharisees quickly left, and meeting with King Herod's supportersÂŠ23517, they conspired to killÂŠ23528 Yeshua.
\s1 Big crowds press on Yeshua
