\v 9 \x + \xo 3:9-10: \xt Mrk 4:1; Luk 5:1-3.\x*SoÂŠ23592 Yeshua asked hisÂŠ23596 apprenticesÂŠ23595 to organise a smallÂŠ23598 boatÂŠ23598 to be there for him so he wouldn't be cramped by the press of the crowdÂŠ23604.
