\v 18 AndrewÂŠ23781, PhilipÂŠ23786, BartholomewÂŠ23789, MatthewÂŠ23791, ThomasÂŠ23794, Yacob Alfaeus, ThaddeusÂŠ23804, SimonÂŠ23806 from Canaan,
\v 19 andÂŠ23814 YudasÂŠ23815 IscariotÂŠ23817 who later betrayed himÂŠ23825.
\s1 The two opposing spiritual powers
