\r (Mat. 12:22-32; Luke 11:14-23; 12:10)
\p
\v 20 ThenÂŠ23826 Yeshua was approaching a houseÂŠ23831, butÂŠ23826 the crowdÂŠ23836 swarmed them againÂŠ23834 so they had no opportunity to eatÂŠ23845.
\v 21 The ones with him heardÂŠ23848 all the noise andÂŠ23846 cameÂŠ23859 to get him, because they were wondering if he was crazy.
\p
\v 22 \x + \xo 3:22: \xt Mat 9:34; 10:25.\x*The religiousÂŠ23872 teachersÂŠ23872 had comeÂŠ23876 up from Yerushalem andÂŠ23870 were complaining, âHe's possessed by the prince of demons. He can command them because he rules them!â
