\q1
\v 12 \x + \xo 4:12: \xt Isa 6:9-10 (LXX).\x*\wj so that when they look they might see but not perceiveÂŠ24478,\wj*
\q1 \wj and when they listen, they might hearÂŠ24480 but not understandÂŠ24485,\wj*
\q1 \wj otherwise they might turnÂŠ24488 \+add from their sins\+add* and be forgivenÂŠ24490.\wj*â
