\v 22 \x + \xo 4:22: \xt Mat 10:26; Luk 12:2.\x*\wj You see, nothing is hiddenÂŠ24729 that won't eventually be disclosed, andÂŠ24736 there'sÂŠ24727 no secretÂŠ24738 that won't eventually be revealedÂŠ24735.\wj*
\v 23 \wj Anyone who wants to understand must listen carefully.\wj*â
\p
\v 24 \x + \xo 4:24: \xt Mat 7:2; Luk 6:38.\x*And heÂŠ24753 continued, â\wj Take care what you listen to. Because how much you judge others, so too will judgement be handed out to you, andÂŠ24752 even more.\wj*
\v 25 \x + \xo 4:25: \xt Mat 13:12; 25:29; Luk 19:26.\x*\wj Anyone who has \+add faith\+add* will be givenÂŠ24776 \+add a reward\+add*, butÂŠ24779 if you have none, even the little you have will be takenÂŠ24786 away.\wj*â
