\v 38 ButÂŠ25057 Yeshua slept on in the back, sleepingÂŠ25069 on a cushionÂŠ25067. They woke him andÂŠ25057 cried, âTeacherÂŠ25078, don'tÂŠ25079 you care that we're all about to drown?â
