\v 9 Yeshua asked, â\wj What'sÂŠ25339 yourÂŠ25342 name?\wj*â
\p The man answered, âMy name is âThousandsâ becauseÂŠ25356 there's many of us,â
\v 10 andÂŠ25359 he begged Yeshua not to sendÂŠ25369 them out of the countryÂŠ25374.
