\v 13 Yeshua agreed to that, so the ungodlyÂŠ25435 spiritsÂŠ25433 came out of the man, wentÂŠ25436 into the pigs, and the entire herd of some two thousandÂŠ25454 pigs rushedÂŠ25442 down the steepÂŠ25447 bank into the sea and were drownedÂŠ25456.
