\v 34 Yeshua saidÂŠ25892, â\wj DaughterÂŠ25895, yourÂŠ25898 faithÂŠ25897 has healedÂŠ25899 you. Go in peaceÂŠ25903 andÂŠ25890 full healthÂŠ25906.\wj*â
