\v 37 And Yeshua didn'tÂŠ25949 allowÂŠ25950 anyoneÂŠ25951 to accompanyÂŠ25961 himÂŠ25956 other than PeterÂŠ25966, and Yacob and his brotherÂŠ25972, Yohan.
