\v 3 Isn't this the carpenterÂŠ26183, the son of MariaÂŠ26188, and the brotherÂŠ26191 of Yacob and Yosef and YudasÂŠ26198 and SimonÂŠ26200? Don't his sistersÂŠ26207 live around here?â And theyÂŠ26214 were offendedÂŠ26214 by his teaching.
