\v 11 \x + \xo 6:11: \xt Acts 13:51.\x*\wj ButÂŠ26364 if any places don't want you or don't want to hearÂŠ26375 what you have to say, just leave that placeÂŠ26369. As you go, shakeÂŠ26380 the dust off yourÂŠ26387 sandals so they can see \+add that you pass the responsibility of what happened to them\+add*.\wj*â
