\v 13 \x + \xo 6:13: \xt Jam 5:14.\x*And they drove out many demonsÂŠ26416, and anointedÂŠ26422 many sickÂŠ26427 people with oliveÂŠ26424 oilÂŠ26424 and healedÂŠ26429 them.
\s1 The execution of Yohan-the-immerser
