\v 55 and ranÂŠ27377 aroundÂŠ27377 that region, so next minute people beganÂŠ27386 bringing all of those who were sickÂŠ27395, carryingÂŠ27397 them on palletsÂŠ27391 to whereverÂŠ27401 they heard that Yeshua was.
\v 56 And whenever Yeshua enteredÂŠ27420 villagesÂŠ27423 or citiesÂŠ27426 or fieldsÂŠ27429 or marketplacesÂŠ27438, they laid the sick down there and were imploringÂŠ27443 him that they might even just touchÂŠ27452 the edge of hisÂŠ27451 robe, and anyone who did so was healedÂŠ27460.
