\v 30 And when sheÂŠ28122 got homeÂŠ28119, the demonÂŠ28140 had indeed gone andÂŠ28115 her littleÂŠ28129 girl was lying quietly on her bed.
\s1 Yeshua heals a deaf man who couldn't speak
