\p
\v 31 Yeshua left the TyreÂŠ28148 region, passed throughÂŠ28150 Tsidon, andÂŠ28142 cameÂŠ28149 down the \add eastern\add* side of the Lake of GalileeÂŠ28159 to the DecapolisÂŠ28167 region.
