\v 2 â\wj I feel sorry for all these people becauseÂŠ28322 they've alreadyÂŠ28323 been with us for threeÂŠ28327 daysÂŠ28324 andÂŠ28336 don'tÂŠ28337 have anythingÂŠ28339 to eatÂŠ28340.\wj*
\v 3 \wj I can't send them homeÂŠ28349 because they're too weak to walk, andÂŠ28341 some have a long way to go.\wj*â
