\p
\v 22 As they entered BethsaidaÂŠ28755, the people brought a blindÂŠ28759 manÂŠ28759 to Yeshua andÂŠ28750 asked him to touchÂŠ28765 him.
\v 23 SoÂŠ28766 Yeshua took the man's handÂŠ28771 and led him out of the villageÂŠ28781. ThenÂŠ28766 he spat in his eyesÂŠ28787, placed his handsÂŠ28792 on him, and asked him, â\wj What can you see?\wj*â
